snippet.title: Get Ready for Dynamax in Pokémon Sword and Pokémon Shield! ⚔️🛡️
snippet.description:
Everything you thought you knew about the world of Pokémon is about to change...in a big way.

Here’s the latest on the exciting new adventure that awaits in Pokémon Sword and Pokémon Shield! 

⚔️🛡️ http://bit.ly/2wJ3Iol
